Global Natural Menthol and Synthetic Menthol Market Insights
Natural Menthol and Synthetic Menthol Market size was valued at USD 0.7 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Natural Menthol and Synthetic Menthol Market Overview
The global Natural Menthol and Synthetic Menthol market was valued at approximately USD 738.8 million in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 942.5 million by 2029, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 3.5% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for menthol in various sectors, including pharmaceuticals, food and beverages, and personal care products. The Asia Pacific region holds the largest market share, accounting for about 58%, followed by Europe and North America. In terms of product type, natural menthol dominates the market with a share exceeding 77%, while the largest application is in oral hygiene, followed by medicinal uses.

